Other classes have defense with or without pets, we are the only ones without.<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Magician pets are also better tanks then their pets. If magicians get root then there is no reason for magician pets to be better defensivly then any other class. In fact, beastlord pets should probobly be alot better then magician pets then. The reliance on pets as defense is the main motivation for magician pets defensive strenght, without that reliance so is there no reason for magicians to have strong pets.<br>
<br>
Similarily, a necromancer needs his spells to keep his pet alive. A mob a magician can just cast DS on pet, pet attack, nuke and mobs dies. A necromancer on the same mob is required to use fearkite to kill it else the pet dies.<br>
<br>
